Description: # ci
        
        Easily run common CI tasks in Python
        
        ## Getting started
        
        Install this package with
        
        ```bash
        pip install ci
        ```
        
        ## Example usage
        
        Run `pip install codecov` only when we are using Python 3.7
        
        ```bash
        ci --only 3.7 pip install codecov
        ```
        
        Run `flake8` on all Python versions except `2.7`
        
        ```bash
        ci --skip 2.7 flake8
        ```
        
